snippet.textDisplay: The Veena section and Vijay Prakash's entry with "jaan udhedoon" followed by his last sargam strike a chord in particular. But all in all a fantastic composition and a masterpiece by Clinton Cerejo. This composition certainly deserves much much more than the 300,000 odd views it has had so far. This has been entrancing me for a while now. I feel rather sad that I got to see this so late. The emotions have been fantastically put through. Electronica plus organic.... Beautiful vibes. I am just not getting tired of listening to this song on repeat. Lastly, I feel very sad for the 53 people who have disliked this.
